Private investigator Andrew Fisch is good at finding people, especially those who don't want to be found.  But when his latest assignment (the seductive wife of a high-level Defense Department scientist) turns up in his best friend's bed, he is thrust into the underbelly of post atomic Los Angeles... where science is king and nothing is as it seems.  What follows is a night of back alley beatings, triplet Russian thugs, and... lightning shooting revoolvers?
